short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sets privacy for Ideone submissions to private by default, alerts user when making a public/secret paste.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
First of all, Ideone is a very good online IDE, if you haven't tried it yet, give it a try, you will love it. 

This extension sets privacy for Ideone submissions to private by default, 
and alerts if user is making a public/secret paste, so that your codes doesnot become public un-intentionally, specially in case of on-going online programming contests and judges.
